title: Add WBTC/WETH Sushi incentives
body:
As discussed on the forum. Uniswap is currently beating Sushiswap in WBTC/WETH liquidity. To incentivize Uniswap LP users to migrate, the protocol needs to add ongoing incentives for the pool. USDC/ETH has 2320 allocation points, and the standard ongoing altcoin/ETH pool has 1000. 

Voting "Yes" indicates to assign WBTC/WETH 1750 allocation points.

Discussion: https://forum.sushiswapclassic.org/t/proposal-adding-wbtc-eth-to-the-common-pool/1124
author: 0xa4214cab2b92900F82a32Ee881D15a8809F764ee
